						               													<description>Zaka is a light-hearted strategy card game set in a magical and monster-filled realm called &amp;quot;Zaka&amp;quot;. In this game, players each build an army of whimsical monsters and then battle their way to victory using their monsters&amp;rsquo; unique abilities and a hoard of dangerous weapons.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This fully self-contained game provides an intuitively easy-to-learn and party-ready spin on the classic genre of fantasy battle card games. To play, each player collects monster cards, upgrades them with compatible weapon cards, then uses their available special abilities to destroy enemy threats and take control of the battlefield. But players must plan their moves carefully to maximise their loot without attracting the wrath of opponent monster armies!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Designed to encourage lots of cheeky player interaction and treachery, this game suits both skilled strategists and first-time gamers alike.'&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
